{"tid":726081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：黑白Benz相殘 鏟水馬空翻落地","createTime":"2018-07-02T06:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T06:33:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"95b7171caeb2866c1cc39a52a770d3dce3a70c33","tid":726081,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:12:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180702/20437669\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180702%2F20437669&d=uLK1R3VyKD4%2BN24X34HBUv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=1741f4d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180702%2F20437669&h=9b90657f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180702/20437669</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月02日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：黑白Benz相殘<br />\n鏟水馬空翻落地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180702/large/a1201b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180702%2Flarge%2Fa1201b.gif&h=d1557aca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n「切勿跟車太貼，時刻保持兩秒距離」，呢個道理似乎唔係人人都明，為咗慳幾秒出事，你話幾唔抵呢！<br />\n<br />\n話說噚日朝早7點幾，粉嶺公路往九龍方向近康樂園有兩架平治（Benz）相撞，仲要搞到封咗兩條行車線，啲車塞到死晒！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n炒車司機擦傷送院<br />\n<br />\n由網民提供嘅車cam片段，清楚拍到事發一刻，當時兩架分別黑、白色嘅平治，喺粉嶺公路快線行駛，尾隨嘅白色平治，緊貼黑色平治行駛，黑車突然收慢，白車收唔切掣撞咗埋去，黑車失控鏟向右邊水馬，360度打咗個觔斗先跌返落地，車cam主人原本喺中線行駛，嚇到大叫「嘩」一聲，好彩佢即時抽去慢線，否則可能三車串燒。<br />\n<br />\n好彩黑色平治上嘅50歲姓吳男司機只係手腳擦傷，仍然清醒，事後由救護員送院治理。而白色平治35歲姓莊司機未有受傷，意外後接受警方調查。受事故影響，現場交通一度擠塞，龍尾長達3公里，去到九龍坑，直至9點半清理完畢先回復正常。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片：色狼影裙底斷正　偽求饒偷刪相<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片：躁女熱到報警　玩謝巴士車長乘客"},{"pid":"69372507945314840ad906d8793ed447ee5d3b4c","tid":726081,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:22:19.000Z","msg":"揸得benz 唔意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0a5c93e9e03e641f546490e4472f34d03d3986","tid":726081,"uid":84355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:24:04.000Z","msg":"咁好鋼水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd35e5149afa086c8c909d0cce1844d40c1a5d3d","tid":726081,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:27:48.000Z","msg":"畀人隊屎忽失控喎, 仲要怪事主? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9688169a2cfedb56011e38c12ee018b0d74439ff","tid":726081,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T06:33:52.000Z","msg":"如果唔係Benz 係GTR 會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}